head.title: Miss Vaiti to Wed Dr. David Moss

hedline.hl1: Miss Vaiti to Wed Dr. David Moss

block.p: The engagement of Vanessa Louise Vaiti and Dr. David Barry Moss has been announced by the prospective bride's parents, Mrs. Stephen J. Zielinski of Shrewsbury, N.J., and Victor F. Vaiti of Allenhurst, N.J. Dr. Moss is a son of Dr. and Mrs. David I. Moss of Allenhurst and Edison, N.J. A May wedding is planned.

Miss Vaiti, 21 years old, graduated from the Tobe-Coburn School and is a student at Georgian Court College. Her father owns and heads North American Computers and Equipment in Edison. Her mother, Nancy Zielinski, is a sales associate with Prudential Realty in Deal, N.J.

Dr. Moss, 27, graduated from St. Bonaventure University and received a D.D.S. degree from New York University. He is a dentist in private practice with his father in Edison. The bridegroom's mother, Andrea P. Moss, is a special-education teacher in the Edison public school system.
